{{language|LaTeX}}'''LaTeX''' is a document preparation language (markup language) written by Lamport (1985, 1994) to allow authors to create documents to be typeset using the [[TeX]] typesetting language (Knuth: 1978, 1982), without having to know the internal details of TeX. For further details please see the links below.

